      "description": "The Defiance Daily Target 2X Long PURR ETF (PUR) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in health care equity. The fund seeks daily investment results, before fees and expenses, of two times (200%) the daily percentage change in the share price of Hyperliquid Strategies Inc (Nasdaq: PURR). PUR was launched on Jul 7, 2026 and is issued by Defiance.",
